title: Pokemon Green Beta: Lavender Town - PaulStretched
description:
Pocket Monsters Beta Green Midori. Lavender Town theme.

The infamous Lavender Town Syndrome theme I have taken and stretched to an hour. It has been slowed down to an hour's length, and boy is it creepy.


Disclaimer: I am not affiliated with GameFreak or Nintendo. Also, this is not the original Lavender Town Syndrome theme. The Syndrome theme is from Pocket Monsters Green Midori, which was a public Japanese release. This particular song was from the non-public Beta of Green. Few gamers have actually heard the Beta LT theme until recent years.

This is my first torrent, and I used some crappy trackers. Hopefully I will get the concept of trackers, since trackers are terrible to acquire. I'm not sure how people get trackers.
